<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1909-02-23T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1909-02-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="364" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d364">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Dawson</persName> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Bogota</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1909-02-23"><hi rend="italic">February 23,
                                    1909</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>The treaties passed reading to-day. The proceedings public. The treaties
                            now are before a special committee. No unfavorable developments so
                            far.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Dawson.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>